{
  "id": "69a7b22c8769b52dc02e2ca4",
  "title": "Jだけ字体おかしくない？",
  "created": 1772597805,
  "updated": 1772634754,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a7b22c8769b52dc02e2ca4",
      "text": "Jだけ字体おかしくない？",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d0000000000575837",
      "text": "from [2026/03/03]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b2c60000000000ab35e1",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/3b98927d9c2a89e2b4f4e77942f0948d]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597958,
      "updated": 1772597959
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d0000000000575838",
      "text": " [J]だけ字体おかしくない？[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597861
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d0000000000575839",
      "text": "  のび～してる[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d000000000057583a",
      "text": "  ちょうど身体を伸ばしだい気分だったんだよ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d000000000057583b",
      "text": " こういうフォントなの？",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d000000000057583c",
      "text": " [Open Sans] のようです。Cosense指定のUIフォントですね[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d000000000057583d",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/61c429eaab455429de9f11e65f9ea4ff]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d000000000057583e",
      "text": " [Open Sans - Google Fonts https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Open+Sans?specimen.preview.text=Noto+CJK+JP]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d000000000057583f",
      "text": " 　どうしてJだけこんな違和感が………[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d0000000000575840",
      "text": "  \tちなみに [Noto Sans] の「J」の字形もほぼ同じ。しかし興味深いことに、[Noto Sans JP] のほうの高さは揃えられている[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d0000000000575841",
      "text": "  \t\t下にはみ出さないJは日本人にとって馴染み深い字形なのかもしれない",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d0000000000575842",
      "text": "  \t\tペン字体の大文字のJが国や地域によってはこのように下にはみ出る字形が主流であることが影響しているのかもしれない（ヨーロッパでは[筆記体]が現役で使われている）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d0000000000575843",
      "text": "  \t\t\t\t気になったのでさっきLLMに食わせてみたやつ https://chatgpt.com/s/t_69a6c020d31881919ac23c0e2f8b8b46",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d0000000000575844",
      "text": "  \t\t\t\tクエリー:`ペン字体の大文字のJが国や地域によってはこのように下にはみ出る字形が主流であることが影響しているのかもしれない（ヨーロッパでは[筆記体]が現役で使われている）`",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d0000000000575845",
      "text": "  \t\t\t\t裏取りまではしてないけどこの回答はたぶんだいたいあってる",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d0000000000575846",
      "text": "  \t\t[https://maiss-schulshop.de/plakat-schulausgangsschrift-sas-2014/4174 https://maiss-schulshop.de/thumbnail/a8/b7/22/1640625182/4174-4174-1_1920x1920.jpg?ts=1640625191]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d0000000000575847",
      "text": " 　じぇ～～～[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d0000000000575848",
      "text": " 　[https://gyazo.com/448de160f7c7b98ece2ad020849d93c6][mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d0000000000575849",
      "text": " 　　[***** [そんな餌で俺様が釣られクマ――.icon]][nomadoor.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d000000000057584a",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/0edb753cd8ec2011552a642528d8833e]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d000000000057584b",
      "text": "　なんか定とか歴だけ字が太い",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d000000000057584c",
      "text": "　拡大率の問題？",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d000000000057584d",
      "text": "　うむむ。とりあえず[Google Fonts https://fonts.google.com/specimen/BIZ+UDGothic?preview.text_type=custom&specimen.preview.text=人類社会のすべての歴史的放火魔、定規、らりるれろ]の表示だけ見てみたけどこの表示にはならなかった [Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d000000000057584e",
      "text": "　\tフォント自身の属性やヒンティングの関係なのかもしれない",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a7b22d000000000057584f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772597805,
      "updated": 1772597805
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8339b0000000000f47811",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/0dbd240ceba39741919bfc440be33552]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772630939,
      "updated": 1772630941
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8339c0000000000f47813",
      "text": " 飯抜も太いかも[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772630941,
      "updated": 1772630964
    },
    {
      "id": "69a840060000000000821ff2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634119,
      "updated": 1772634119
    },
    {
      "id": "69a840060000000000821ff3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634119,
      "updated": 1772634119
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8400e0000000000821ff5",
      "text": "[- 調べてみましたが、よくわかりませんでした[Nrem.icon]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634127,
      "updated": 1772634162
    },
    {
      "id": "69a840630000000000821ff9",
      "text": " \tフォントのことをよく知らないので自分が全然関係のないところの話をしている可能性がある",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634212,
      "updated": 1772634344
    },
    {
      "id": "69a840940000000000821ffa",
      "text": "\tこの記述が気になる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634261,
      "updated": 1772634329
    },
    {
      "id": "69a840060000000000821ff4",
      "text": "  https://github.com/googlefonts/morisawa-biz-ud-gothic/pull/29",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634119,
      "updated": 1772634355
    },
    {
      "id": "69a840590000000000821ff7",
      "text": "  > 4.41.1 (released 2023-07-21)",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634201,
      "updated": 1772634355
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8405b0000000000821ff8",
      "text": "  > 【…】",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634203,
      "updated": 1772634355
    },
    {
      "id": "69a840380000000000821ff6",
      "text": "  > `[statisticsPen]` Report font glyph-average weight/width and font-wide slant.",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634169,
      "updated": 1772634365
    },
    {
      "id": "69a842810000000000822002",
      "text": "  \t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634754,
      "updated": 1772634754
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8413f0000000000821ffb",
      "text": "  自分がフォント周りの基礎的な知識が抜けているので、この一行を試しにLLMに投げてどのような反応をするのかを見た。何の取っ掛かりもないよりはいいだろう",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634432,
      "updated": 1772634704
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8418a0000000000821ffc",
      "text": "  https://chatgpt.com/share/69a84191-eb18-8011-afd6-b70ebb57999d",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634506,
      "updated": 1772634524
    },
    {
      "id": "69a841970000000000821ffe",
      "text": "  > まず glyph-average weight（字形平均ウェイト）ですが、これは各グリフの黒画素面積（inked area）をそのグリフのエム平方（em square）またはバウンディングボックス面積で正規化し、対象文字集合（通常はA–Z, a–z, 0–9 など）に対して平均した値です。単位は相対比率（例：0.18 ＝ 18%塗りつぶし）で表します。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634520,
      "updated": 1772634524
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8418d0000000000821ffd",
      "text": "  > 式の概念形は次の通りです。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634509,
      "updated": 1772634509
    },
    {
      "id": "69a841d60000000000821fff",
      "text": "  > 平均ウェイト = (Σ inked_area_i / box_area_i) / N",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634582,
      "updated": 1772634616
    },
    {
      "id": "69a841f80000000000822000",
      "text": "  > 次に glyph-average width（平均字幅）は、各グリフの advance width を units per em で正規化し平均を取ります。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634616,
      "updated": 1772634616
    },
    {
      "id": "69a841f80000000000822001",
      "text": "  > 平均字幅 = (Σ advance_width_i / UPM) / N",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772634616,
      "updated": 1772634616
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8339c0000000000f47812",
      "text": "\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772630941,
      "updated": 1772634627
    }
  ]
}